                    <h1>Additional Topics</h1>
                    <section>
                        <h4>Editing files in the command line</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>vi</li>
                            <li>vim</li>
                            <li>nano</li>
                            <li>emacs</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div style="margin-top=2em;"><a href="http://vim-adventures.com/" target="_blank">vim-adventures</a></div>
                    </section>
                    <section>
                        <h4>Running Scheduled Tasks with Cron Jobs</h4>
                        <p>added by editing the cron file</p>
                        <p>specify the schedule you want to run on and the script or command you want to run</p>
                        <pre><code>* * * * * <span style="color:red;">command to be executed</span>
| | | | |_ day of week (0 - 6, 0 = Sunday)
| | | |___ month (1 - 12)
| | |_____ day of month (1 - 31)
| |_______ hour (0 - 23)
|_________ minute (0 - 59)</code></pre>
                    </section>
